    A Wonderful Mall Located Outside of Lisbon City Center
    Our server at Benfica 409 restaurant told us about this mall. We were so glad he did!!! To get there on the Metro from Lisbon City Center, take the blue line in the direction of Linha Azul and get off at the Military College Station/Luz station. We found better prices on food, wine, etc. here at the Continente grocery store, which is a very large store. We visited here twice during our stay in Lisbon.
